    System time:	dfaa2c15.2083126e  Thu, Nov 29 2018 18:12:53.127
    Atomic time:	dfaa2c15.210624dd  Thu, Nov 29 2018 18:12:53.129


[1]: https://github.com/apache/commons-net
[2]: https://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-net/javadocs/api-3.6/org/apache/commons/net/ntp/NTPUDPClient.html
[3]: https://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-net/javadocs/api-3.6/org/apache/commons/net/ntp/TimeInfo.html

