{ &quot;aggregate&quot; : &quot;__collection__&quot;, &quot;pipeline&quot; : [{ &quot;$match&quot; : { &quot;update&quot; : { &quot;$in&quot; : [{ &quot;import_created_at&quot; : 1661784425743}]}}}........


